    <published>2022-10-19T08:56:06.835Z</published>
    <updated>2024-07-21T07:50:38.519Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="步骤"><a href="#步骤" class="headerlink" title="步骤"></a>步骤</h1><ol><li>拉取镜像</li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker pull cassandra:latest</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="./cassadra/pull.png" alt=""></p><ol><li>创建网络</li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker network create cassandra</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>此处获取网络编号 ：76ca96758205d4481bc36ba4eb3a2665c0856ac8e9cc7ec2a321ba011b739041</p><ol><li>启动容器</li></ol><figure class="highlight docker"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker <span class="keyword">run</span><span class="language-bash"> --name cassandra -d -p 9042:9042 -v /Users/cassandra/conf/cassandra.yaml:/etc/cassandra/cassandra.yaml -v /Users/cassandra/data:/var/lib/cassandra --hostname cassandra --network cassandra cassandra</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>docker run —name cassandra1 -d -p 9042:9042  -v /Users/cassandra/data:/var/lib/cassandra —hostname cassandra —network cassandra cassandra</p><p>docker run —name cassandra -p 9042:9042 -v /Users/cassandra/conf/cassandra.yaml:/etc/cassandra/cassandra.yaml -v /Users/cassandra/data:/var/lib/cassandra -d —restart=always </p><ul><li>—name（容器名字）</li><li>-d 守护进程，后台运行该容器</li><li>-p（端口） 主机(宿主)端口:容器端口</li><li>-v （目录映射）主机(宿主)配置地址:容器配置地址<br>例如：yaml</li><li>—network网络</li><li>–restart 是否重启  always<h3 id="进入容器"><a href="#进入容器" class="headerlink" title="进入容器"></a>进入容器</h3></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker run -it --network cassandra  --<span class="built_in">rm</span> cassandra cqlsh cassandra</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker <span class="built_in">cp</span> /Users/yutaima/Desktop/exp4cassandra/2023-cassandra实践工具软件及测试数据 cassandra:/etc/cassandra</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="./cassadra/run.png" alt="启动后自己蹦出来一个？"></p><p><img src="./cassadra/terminal.png" alt="终端界面"></p><p>Connection error: (‘Unable to connect to any servers’, {‘172.18.0.2:9042’: ConnectionRefusedError(111, “Tried connecting to [(‘172.18.0.2’, 9042)]. Last error: Connection refused”)})</p><p>docker exec -it cassandra bash</p><p>docker exec -it cassandra cqlsh</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
